text: Desmiphora cucullata is a species of beetle in the family Cerambycidae. It was described by Thomson in 1868. It is known from Argentina, Brazil, Paraguay, and Uruguay.BioLib.cz - Desmiphora cucullata. Retrieved on 8 September 2014. ==References== Category:Desmiphora Category:Beetles described in 1868
